WEBVTT

00:06.207 --> 00:08.142
[footsteps approaching]

00:29.630 --> 00:31.332
- BRING HIM DOWN!

00:45.513 --> 00:48.416
- I GAVE YOU A CHOICE THAT DAY.
[chains rattling]

00:48.449 --> 00:50.418
THAT BOY DIDN'T HAVE TO HANG.

00:50.451 --> 00:54.422
- NO, HE DIDN'T.

00:54.455 --> 00:59.193
BUT YOU DO, FOR ALL YOU DONE.

01:50.911 --> 01:54.348
- THE COUNCIL WELCOMES
BISHOP JOSEPH DUTSON.

01:59.220 --> 02:01.489
- PLEASE BE SEATED.

02:03.324 --> 02:04.592
- MY GOD.

02:04.625 --> 02:06.627
[chains rattle]

02:06.660 --> 02:08.396
- WHY HAS HEAVENLY FATHER

02:08.429 --> 02:11.699
BROUGHT THIS MAN
BEFORE ME TODAY?

02:18.672 --> 02:21.642
[western folk music]

02:21.675 --> 02:29.683
*

02:51.705 --> 02:56.677
- THE CHARGES INCLUDE MURDER,
TRESPASS, AND SEDITION.

02:58.712 --> 03:00.581
- STATE YOUR NAME,

03:00.614 --> 03:02.616
FOR THE COUNCIL.

03:05.986 --> 03:08.689
- THE BISHOP ASKED YOU
TO STATE YOUR NAME.

03:10.558 --> 03:12.393
- UNH!

03:12.426 --> 03:13.727
- [gasps]
- OH!

03:13.761 --> 03:17.565
[both grunting]

03:17.598 --> 03:18.666
- I KILLED YOU,
YOU SON OF A BITCH!

03:18.699 --> 03:19.700
YOU'RE DEAD!

03:19.733 --> 03:21.302
- GET OFF HIM!

03:21.335 --> 03:22.636
- [chokes, sputters]
- GET OFF HIM!

03:22.670 --> 03:24.405
- [grunts]
- [gasps]

03:24.438 --> 03:26.407
[coughs]

03:26.440 --> 03:28.309
- [grunting, fighting]

03:28.342 --> 03:30.578
OH!
OH!

03:30.611 --> 03:32.746
[groans]

03:32.780 --> 03:34.982
- OH, MY GOD.
- BACK UP, BACK UP.

03:35.015 --> 03:36.717
- [coughs]
[overlapping chatter]

03:40.053 --> 03:42.456
[coughs]

03:42.490 --> 03:43.557
- DAMN YOU!

03:43.591 --> 03:47.027
AND YOUR OVERZEALOUS MILITIA!

03:47.060 --> 03:49.563
BRINGING YET ANOTHER VIPER...

03:49.597 --> 03:50.698
- [gasps]

03:50.731 --> 03:52.600
- TO OUR HOLY HOUSE.

03:52.633 --> 03:54.668
- [gasps]

03:54.702 --> 03:58.606
[grunts, sniffles]

03:58.639 --> 04:01.475
- I WILL ASK AGAIN, HMM?

04:04.445 --> 04:07.448
YOUR NAME?

04:07.481 --> 04:10.451
- THOR GUNDERSON.

04:10.484 --> 04:12.753
- [coughs]

04:12.786 --> 04:14.522
WRITE THAT DOWN.
"THOR GUNDERSON."

04:14.555 --> 04:17.491
- THAT'S HIS NAME.
HIS REAL NAME.

04:17.525 --> 04:19.660
- THIS IS BISHOP JOSEPH DUTSON.

04:19.693 --> 04:23.030
- MMM, NO.

04:23.063 --> 04:25.433
GOES BY "THE SWEDE" BACK EAST.

04:25.466 --> 04:27.401
MURDERER OF INNOCENT MEN
AND WOMEN.

04:27.435 --> 04:30.571
- HE IS ELDER OF THE HIGHEST
PRIESTHOOD OFFICE!

04:30.604 --> 04:32.706
HE IS PRESIDENT
OF THE PRIESTS' QUORUM,

04:32.740 --> 04:33.807
AND FATHER OF THE WARD!

04:33.841 --> 04:35.676
- HE'S EVIL.

04:35.709 --> 04:37.778
THAT MAN RIGHT THERE,
HE'S EVIL, I'M TELLING YOU.

04:37.811 --> 04:39.747
- PERHAPS YOU MISTAKE HIM
FOR SOMEONE ELSE.

04:39.780 --> 04:42.383
- NO, THAT'S HIM.
- WHO GAVE YOU AUTHORITY

04:42.416 --> 04:45.586
TO DIGNIFY
THIS GENTILE'S LIES?

04:45.619 --> 04:47.621
- BUT--
- DO YOU PRESIDE OVER THIS WARD?

04:51.859 --> 04:54.462
THEN YOU SPEAK WHEN SPOKEN TO,
HMM?

04:54.495 --> 04:56.797
GOOD.

04:56.830 --> 04:59.400
BLASPHEMING IN
THE GATHERING PLACE

04:59.433 --> 05:05.072
OF THE KINGDOM OF GOD
IS A CRIME.

05:05.105 --> 05:07.775
HEAVENLY FATHER DECIDES
WHEN A MAN IS

05:07.808 --> 05:11.645
TO BE TAKEN FROM THIS LIFE.

05:11.679 --> 05:15.516
AND BE AWARE, BE ADVISED,

05:15.549 --> 05:18.686
THAT I HAVE BEEN ANOINTED
BY HIM,

05:18.719 --> 05:23.090
AND APPOINTED WITH THE POWER
AND THE KEYS OF THE PRIESTHOOD.

05:23.123 --> 05:28.562
YOUR FATE IS IN MY HANDS.

05:32.400 --> 05:35.102
NOW...

05:35.135 --> 05:40.574
I ASK AGAIN...YOUR NAME?

05:41.942 --> 05:45.613
- YOU KNOW MY NAME.

05:45.646 --> 05:51.485
[indistinct chatter]

05:52.953 --> 05:55.823
- MR. FERGUSON.

05:57.157 --> 05:59.359
ARE YOU HEADING BACK
TO THE CUT?

06:02.596 --> 06:06.400
YOU'RE CHIEF
OF RAILROAD POLICE.

06:06.434 --> 06:10.571
MR. BOHANNON IS GONE.
YOU NEED TO DO SOMETHING!

06:10.604 --> 06:12.606
DAMN YOU!

06:15.443 --> 06:18.646
- YOU GOT A MOUTH ON YOU
FOR A CHURCH LADY.

06:25.519 --> 06:27.521
- YOU SHOULD HAVE GONE
AFTER HIM.

06:30.190 --> 06:32.860
I THOUGHT YOU WERE HIS FRIEND.

06:34.995 --> 06:38.766
HOW WILL YOU FEEL
AT HIS FUNERAL?

06:38.799 --> 06:41.669
- AIN'T GONNA BE NO FUNERAL.

06:47.675 --> 06:50.778
- MR. BOHANNON SAT IN MY HOME,

06:50.811 --> 06:53.914
SHARED A MEAL WITH MY FAMILY,

06:53.947 --> 06:57.451
AND THEN TOOK EVERYTHING
WE HAD,

06:57.485 --> 06:59.186
INCLUDING MY SON'S LIFE.

06:59.219 --> 07:01.188
- AFTER YOU MURDERED
MY CHIEF OF POLICE.

07:01.221 --> 07:03.223
- I TOLD YOU,

07:03.256 --> 07:04.558
STAY OFF MY LAND!
- [laughs]

07:04.592 --> 07:06.226
ALL RIGHT, CAN I JUST--

07:06.259 --> 07:10.464
CAN I--DAMN IT!
CAN I TALK?

07:10.498 --> 07:11.765
NOW THERE'S LOTS OF THINGS
I DONE

07:11.799 --> 07:12.866
SHOULD HAVE ENDED IN
A HANGMAN'S NOOSE,

07:12.900 --> 07:16.570
AND THIS AIN'T ONE OF 'EM.

07:16.604 --> 07:18.806
HE AIN'T TOLD YOU
THE WHOLE TRUTH.

07:18.839 --> 07:22.810
- NO, I HAVEN'T.

07:22.843 --> 07:24.845
STAND UP, DAUGHTER.

07:29.016 --> 07:31.719
IS THIS THE MAN
WHO VIOLATED YOU?

07:36.924 --> 07:38.959
- HE IS THE FATHER
OF MY CHILD.

07:43.797 --> 07:47.234
- THIS COUNCIL HAS HEARD ENOUGH.

07:47.267 --> 07:52.806
I WILL DELIBERATE
ON A JUST PUNISHMENT...

07:52.840 --> 07:57.878
AS REVEALED
BY HEAVENLY FATHER.

08:17.297 --> 08:19.499
- THEY HURT YOU BAD?

08:21.301 --> 08:24.805
- NO.

08:24.838 --> 08:26.840
YOU?

08:26.874 --> 08:29.943
- I TOLD THEM I WASN'T FORCED.

08:29.977 --> 08:32.312
I WANTED YOU TO KNOW.

08:32.345 --> 08:35.749
- APPRECIATE THAT.

08:35.783 --> 08:37.885
GUESS IT DON'T MAKE
MUCH DIFFERENCE NOW.

08:37.918 --> 08:41.622
- IT DOES TO ME.

08:41.655 --> 08:43.657
IT WILL TO THIS UNBORN.

08:47.060 --> 08:50.898
I KNOW WHAT
YOU MUST BE THINKING.

08:50.931 --> 08:52.933
THIS CHILD IS YOURS.

09:01.108 --> 09:04.544
- CAN, UM...

09:06.714 --> 09:08.716
MAY I TOUCH IT?

09:32.039 --> 09:34.074
- LATELY, I CAN FEEL IT MOVE.

09:45.653 --> 09:48.088
- EVA!

09:48.121 --> 09:50.858
EVA!

09:50.891 --> 09:53.093
EVA!

09:53.126 --> 09:55.362
- YOU TRYING TO GET ME
THROWN OUT OF HERE?

09:55.395 --> 09:56.997
WHAT YOU DOING
WITH ALL THEM GUNS?

09:57.030 --> 09:59.366
- I THINK THE MORMONS
GOT BOHANNON AT FORT SMITH.

09:59.399 --> 10:01.101
I'M GONNA BUST HIM OUT.

10:01.134 --> 10:03.704
- YOU'RE GOING ALONE
THROUGH INDIAN TERRITORY

10:03.737 --> 10:05.405
TO A MORMON FORT?

10:05.438 --> 10:07.107
THAT DON'T MAKE SENSE.

10:07.140 --> 10:09.076
- IT AIN'T MAKE NO SENSE
FOR HIM TO STOP THE RAILROAD

10:09.109 --> 10:11.879
TO LOOK FOR MY BABY,
BUT HE DONE IT.

10:15.448 --> 10:16.984
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE, THEN?

10:17.017 --> 10:21.154
- I JUST WANTED TO SAY...

10:21.188 --> 10:25.726
I DON'T KNOW WHY
YOU DONE WHAT YOU DONE.

10:25.759 --> 10:28.762
GUESS YOU THOUGHT
IT WAS THE RIGHT THING.

10:33.701 --> 10:37.871
- DON'T GO.

10:37.905 --> 10:41.875
- I GOT TO.

10:41.909 --> 10:46.146
- ELAM.
ELAM!

10:46.179 --> 10:48.849
PLEASE.

10:48.882 --> 10:51.885
I GOT A BAD FEELING.

10:51.919 --> 10:54.154
PLEASE, STAY?

10:54.187 --> 10:56.056
- HYAH!
COME ON!

11:03.130 --> 11:04.832
[indistinct chatter]

11:04.865 --> 11:06.166
- MRS. PALMER, I BELIEVE THIS

11:06.199 --> 11:09.737
TO BE THE FINEST STAIRCASE
IN THE DAKOTA TERRITORY.

11:09.770 --> 11:11.739
- I BELIEVE THIS TO BE
THE ONLY STAIRCASE

11:11.772 --> 11:14.908
IN THE DAKOTA TERRITORY,
MR. DURANT.

11:14.942 --> 11:17.144
- YOU LOOK LIKE A QUEEN.

11:17.177 --> 11:19.179
- AND YOU LOOK LIKE
AN OLD, TICK-FEVERED HOUND.

11:19.212 --> 11:21.815
YOU'VE WON NEW YORK.

11:21.849 --> 11:23.150
WHY SO DOWN IN THE MOUTH?

11:23.183 --> 11:26.920
- I HAVEN'T WON ANYTHING YET.

11:26.954 --> 11:29.122
BOHANNON HAS
AN IRRITATING HABIT

11:29.156 --> 11:32.159
OF SLIPPING OUT
OF TIGHT SPOTS.

11:32.192 --> 11:33.861
- HMM.
[door opens]

11:33.894 --> 11:36.196
- AH!
HMM.

11:36.229 --> 11:40.768
OUR HUMBLE RAILROAD TOWN
HAS FINALLY ARRIVED.

11:40.801 --> 11:45.072
GENERAL GRANT, CHAIRMAN AMES,
MISS ELLISON,

11:45.105 --> 11:49.176
MAY I INTRODUCE THE PROPRIETOR
OF THIS FINE ESTABLISHMENT,

11:49.209 --> 11:51.745
MRS. MARGARET PALMER.

11:51.779 --> 11:53.213
- WELCOME TO CHEYENNE,
GENTLEMEN.

11:53.246 --> 11:55.482
- PLEASURE TO MEET YOU,
MRS. PALMER.

11:55.515 --> 11:57.217
- OH, WELL,
THE PLEASURE IS MINE, GENERAL.

11:57.250 --> 11:59.186
I DO HOPE YOUR STAY WITH US
WILL BE COMFORTABLE.

11:59.219 --> 12:04.191
- SO FAR, THERE IS MUCH
TO RECOMMEND IT.

12:04.224 --> 12:06.526
CONGRATULATIONS ON
AN EXCELLENT INVESTMENT.

12:06.559 --> 12:08.495
- I HAVE TO HAND IT TO YOU,
THOMAS.

12:08.528 --> 12:10.831
THE TOWN APPEARS
TO BE EVERYTHING YOU PROMISED.

12:10.864 --> 12:13.233
- YES, IF YOU AND BOHANNON
WOULD DISPENSE WITH THE MUTUAL

12:13.266 --> 12:16.169
PETTINESS, YOU MIGHT BE FAVORED
WITH GREATNESS.

12:16.203 --> 12:17.971
- WHERE IS MR. BOHANNON?

12:18.005 --> 12:19.506
- IT'S A FEW HOURS EARLY
FOR HIS DEADLINE,

12:19.539 --> 12:21.875
BUT I HAVE A BOTTLE OF BOURBON

12:21.909 --> 12:23.977
AND A BOX OF CIGARS
I'D LIKE TO OPEN.

12:24.011 --> 12:25.312
- WELL, I'M AFRAID
WE WILL HAVE TO MARK

12:25.345 --> 12:28.281
THIS MILESTONE
WITHOUT MR. BOHANNON.

12:28.315 --> 12:30.083
YOU ALL MISSED
QUITE AN ADVENTURE.

12:30.117 --> 12:34.087
MASKED BANDITS TURNED OUR TOWN
INTO A SHOOTING GALLERY,

12:34.121 --> 12:37.224
BEFORE SNATCHING MR. BOHANNON
AND DRAGGING HIM AWAY.

12:37.257 --> 12:38.558
- WITH YOUR PERMISSION,
GENERAL,

12:38.591 --> 12:40.127
I'LL TELEGRAPH THE FORT
AND ORDER

12:40.160 --> 12:41.995
MORE TROOPS FOR YOUR ESCORT.

12:42.029 --> 12:45.332
- I KILLED ONE OF HIS ABDUCTORS
AT CLOSE RANGE,

12:45.365 --> 12:47.234
AND I ALSO MANAGED
TO SAVE A CHILD.

12:47.267 --> 12:49.837
- WE WERE OUTGUNNED,
PLAIN AND SIMPLE.

12:49.870 --> 12:52.172
WE DID EVERYTHING WE COULD
FOR MR. BOHANNON,

12:52.205 --> 12:55.008
EVEN AT GREAT DANGER
TO OURSELVES,

12:55.042 --> 12:57.044
ESPECIALLY MR. DURANT.

13:00.047 --> 13:01.882
NOW LET ME SHOW YOU
TO YOUR ROOM, GENERAL.

13:01.915 --> 13:03.316
AND WHAT CAN I GET YOU
TO DRINK?

13:03.350 --> 13:05.385
- BOURBON, MADAME.
A DOUBLE.

13:12.993 --> 13:15.262
HE HAS UNTIL 6:00.

13:15.295 --> 13:17.797
THERE'S STILL TIME.

13:23.203 --> 13:26.206
- YOU GOT ANY LAST WORDS,
YOU BE A MAN.

13:26.239 --> 13:28.041
SAY 'EM TO ME,
NOT MY DAUGHTER.

13:28.075 --> 13:29.576
YOU DONE ENOUGH TO NAOMI.

13:29.609 --> 13:32.946
- BEEN DOING
SOME HARD THINKING.

13:32.980 --> 13:34.314
I WANNA MAKE THINGS RIGHT.

13:34.347 --> 13:36.950
- YOU WERE MY GUEST.

13:36.984 --> 13:39.152
I GAVE YOU SHELTER.

13:39.186 --> 13:41.121
AND YOU REPAID THE KINDNESS

13:41.154 --> 13:43.190
BY STRIPPING
MY MOST BELOVED DAUGHTER

13:43.223 --> 13:45.592
OF HER CHASTITY AND VIRTUE.

13:45.625 --> 13:48.061
NOW SHE'LL LIVE THIS LIFE
IN SHAME

13:48.095 --> 13:50.630
AND SPEND ETERNITY
IN OUTER DARKNESS.

13:50.663 --> 13:53.200
NO GOD-FEARING MAN
WILL HAVE HER.

13:53.233 --> 13:56.169
- I'LL HAVE HER.
I'LL MARRY HER.

13:56.203 --> 13:57.604
IF SHE'LL HAVE ME.

13:57.637 --> 14:00.340
- NO. I WILL NOT
LET HER BE A PARTY

14:00.373 --> 14:03.176
TO YOUR COWARD'S ATTEMPT
TO ESCAPE JUSTICE.

14:03.210 --> 14:05.612
- I AIN'T A COWARD, SIR.

14:05.645 --> 14:09.349
I'M THAT CHILD'S FATHER.

14:09.382 --> 14:11.384
I'LL STAY HERE
AT FORT SMITH

14:11.418 --> 14:12.385
TILL THE CHILD'S BORN
AND OUR FIRST CROPS

14:12.419 --> 14:14.087
ARE IN THE GROUND.

14:14.121 --> 14:16.223
NOW, YOU HAVE MY WORD:

14:16.256 --> 14:19.026
I'LL GIVE THEM A GOOD
AND HONEST LIFE.

14:19.059 --> 14:21.628
I AIN'T NEVER BROKE MY WORD
TO YOU FOR ILL OR NAUGHT,

14:21.661 --> 14:23.897
AND YOU KNOW THAT.

14:23.931 --> 14:27.634
- SHE WAS MY JOY.

14:27.667 --> 14:29.402
SHE COULD HAVE MARRIED
A BISHOP

14:29.436 --> 14:32.005
OR AN APOSTLE.

14:32.039 --> 14:35.008
BRIGHAM YOUNG HIMSELF
WOULD HAVE BEEN PROUD

14:35.042 --> 14:38.011
TO CALL HER HIS WIFE.

14:38.045 --> 14:41.014
BUT NOW...

14:41.048 --> 14:45.919
HER ONLY SUITOR
IS A GENTILE.

14:45.953 --> 14:47.955
AND A KILLER.

14:56.296 --> 14:58.898
I WILL SEEK COUNSEL.

15:00.433 --> 15:03.903
BUT THE BISHOP'S WORD
IS FINAL.

15:27.094 --> 15:28.495
- SHIT.

15:32.465 --> 15:34.534
[cocks gun]

15:40.207 --> 15:42.309
HYAH!

15:42.342 --> 15:45.412
[men shouting]

15:51.318 --> 15:54.287
[gunshots]

15:56.156 --> 15:58.491
[gunshots]

16:03.096 --> 16:04.397
[gunshot]
- [grunts]

16:08.235 --> 16:10.037
[arrow whizzes, gunshot]

16:12.039 --> 16:13.273
- COME ON!

16:13.306 --> 16:16.076
COME AT ME,
OR GET THE HELL OUT MY WAY.

16:38.498 --> 16:42.169
- I'VE BEEN PRAYING
FOR YOUR SOUL.

16:44.237 --> 16:45.772
- YOU CAN DROP
THE PIOUS BULLSHIT

16:45.805 --> 16:48.141
AND THE PHONY ACCENT.

16:48.175 --> 16:50.143
WE BOTH KNOW YOU'RE THAT SWEDISH
SON OF A BITCH,

16:50.177 --> 16:51.278
THOR GUNDERSEN.

16:51.311 --> 16:54.514
- THOR GUNDERSEN
WAS NORWEGIAN.

16:54.547 --> 16:57.117
AND HE WAS A TROUBLED SOUL...

16:57.150 --> 16:59.386
WHO FELL FROM A BRIDGE
IN NEBRASKA.

16:59.419 --> 17:00.553
- NOT FAR ENOUGH.

17:00.587 --> 17:04.157
- AND I AM BISHOP
JOSEPH DUTSON,

17:04.191 --> 17:07.794
REBORN IN THE HOLY
BAPTISMAL WATERS

17:07.827 --> 17:12.465
AND BLESSED WITH THE GIFT
OF THE HOLY SPIRIT.

17:12.499 --> 17:15.268
- YOU'RE A BLOODTHIRSTY
MURDERER.

17:15.302 --> 17:19.439
- YOU ARE NOT WITHOUT SIN...
MR. BOHANNON.

17:22.309 --> 17:24.511
IT DOES NOT MATTER
WHAT YOU BELIEVE.

17:24.544 --> 17:27.347
I AM BISHOP HERE,

17:27.380 --> 17:30.117
AND I HAVE HAD A REVELATION...

17:30.150 --> 17:32.319
ON THE SUBJECT
OF YOUR FATE.

17:37.357 --> 17:40.593
- I AIN'T GONNA HANG, AM I?

17:40.627 --> 17:42.462
- WHAT MAKES YOU
BELIEVE THAT?

17:42.495 --> 17:44.597
THOSE GALLOWS ARE STRONG.

17:44.631 --> 17:49.402
THE ROPE SECURE.

17:49.436 --> 17:52.172
- I'M MARRYING
HATCH'S DAUGHTER.

17:52.205 --> 17:54.307
- I'M THE ARBITER
OF THE LAW HERE,

17:54.341 --> 17:55.875
NOT BROTHER HATCH.

17:55.908 --> 17:58.278
- NO, I'VE SEEN A DOZEN MEN
STAKE THEIR LIVES

17:58.311 --> 18:00.347
ON HIS WORD, NOT YOURS.

18:00.380 --> 18:02.215
BESIDES...

18:02.249 --> 18:03.616
GOT THE FEELING YOU AIN'T
REAL POPULAR AROUND HERE.

18:03.650 --> 18:05.452
- NOW, WHY WOULD YOU
SAY THAT?

18:05.485 --> 18:07.354
- YOU ALWAYS AIN'T POPULAR
WHEREVER YOU TURN UP.

18:07.387 --> 18:10.223
- MY CREDIBILITY HERE
IS MORE SECURE

18:10.257 --> 18:12.459
THAN YOURS HAS EVER BEEN.

18:12.492 --> 18:13.493
- MAYBE.

18:13.526 --> 18:15.128
BUT I GOT THE FEELING

18:15.162 --> 18:17.364
YOU DONE SOMETHING REAL BAD
TO END UP HERE.

18:17.397 --> 18:19.899
TRUTH CAN'T BE FAR BEHIND.

18:19.932 --> 18:22.335
THAT AIN'T THE REAL REASON
YOU AIN'T GONNA HANG ME.

18:22.369 --> 18:23.870
- HMM.

18:23.903 --> 18:27.607
- REAL REASON IS...

18:27.640 --> 18:31.278
YOU CAN ONLY KILL ME ONCE.

18:31.311 --> 18:34.414
THAT AIN'T GONNA BE
GOOD ENOUGH FOR YOU, IS IT?

18:34.447 --> 18:36.283
YOU'D DRUTHER SEE ME
SUFFER AND DIE,

18:36.316 --> 18:39.252
LITTLE BY LITTLE,
EACH DAY.

18:39.286 --> 18:42.622
- YES.

18:42.655 --> 18:46.259
BUT HEAVENLY FATHER

18:46.293 --> 18:49.396
WISHES TO SEE...
YOU LIVE.

18:51.398 --> 18:54.201
[chuckles]

18:55.702 --> 18:59.272
[laughing]

18:59.306 --> 19:02.342
- MR. CULLEN BOHANNON
IS IN ABSENTIA.

19:02.375 --> 19:06.646
AND, AS THE LARGEST
SINGLE SHAREHOLDER

19:06.679 --> 19:09.382
OF CREDIT MOBILIER STOCK,

19:09.416 --> 19:15.255
I PROPOSE THAT ALL FURTHER
CONTRACTS AND CONSTRUCTION

19:15.288 --> 19:20.527
BE ASSIGNED TO ME,
THOMAS C. DURANT.

19:20.560 --> 19:22.295
DO I HAVE A SECOND?

19:28.568 --> 19:32.672
VERY WELL.

19:32.705 --> 19:35.408
THEN THIS WILL BE
THE TERMINUS

19:35.442 --> 19:37.410
OF THE UNION PACIFIC
RAILROAD!

19:37.444 --> 19:40.947
THIS ENTERPRISE
SHALL END HERE!

19:40.980 --> 19:42.582
- I SECOND.

19:47.520 --> 19:49.389
- [sighs]

19:49.422 --> 19:51.224
AYE.

19:52.559 --> 19:55.562
- ALL OPPOSED?

19:55.595 --> 20:01.434
[men grumbling]

20:01.468 --> 20:03.570
MOTION CARRIED.

20:03.603 --> 20:05.272
IN THE POWERS VESTED IN ME

20:05.305 --> 20:06.573
AS CHAIRMAN
OF CREDIT MOBILIER,

20:06.606 --> 20:09.376
I HEREBY CONFER
ALL FURTHER CONSTRUCTION

20:09.409 --> 20:10.443
OF THE UNION PACIFIC,

20:10.477 --> 20:12.412
FROM THIS SPOT FORWARD,

20:12.445 --> 20:15.282
TO THE CHARGE
OF THOMAS C. DURANT.

20:15.315 --> 20:18.351
[men grumbling]

20:28.027 --> 20:31.364
[chains clinking]

20:43.643 --> 20:45.778
- SHE'S YOURS.

20:49.382 --> 20:52.018
- DO YOU WANT TO BE MINE?

20:52.051 --> 20:55.588
- YES.

20:55.622 --> 20:58.525
IT'S GOD'S WILL.

21:01.093 --> 21:04.764
- WELL...

21:04.797 --> 21:06.866
ALL RIGHT, THEN.
LET'S DO IT.

21:17.610 --> 21:19.579
- SISTER NAOMI,

21:19.612 --> 21:25.418
DO YOU RECEIVE THIS MAN
TO BE YOUR WEDDED HUSBAND,

21:25.452 --> 21:28.855
OBSERVING THE LEGAL RIGHTS
BELONGING

21:28.888 --> 21:31.391
TO THIS CONDITION FOR TIME

21:31.424 --> 21:35.528
AND ALL ETERNITY?

21:35.562 --> 21:39.065
- I DO.

21:39.098 --> 21:41.401
- BROTHER CULLEN,

21:41.434 --> 21:44.737
DO YOU RECEIVE THIS WOMAN

21:44.771 --> 21:46.506
TO BE YOUR WEDDED WIFE,

21:46.539 --> 21:48.841
OBSERVING ALL THE LEGAL RIGHTS

21:48.875 --> 21:50.710
BELONGING TO THIS CONDITION

21:50.743 --> 21:55.748
FOR TIME AND ALL ETERNITY?

21:57.417 --> 21:58.818
- I DO.

21:58.851 --> 22:02.689
- IN THE NAME
OF THE LORD JESUS CHRIST,

22:02.722 --> 22:05.458
AND BY VIRTUE OF THE LAWS
OF COUNTRY

22:05.492 --> 22:09.128
AND AUTHORITY VESTED IN ME,

22:09.161 --> 22:12.765
I PRONOUNCE YOU...

22:12.799 --> 22:15.735
HUSBAND...

22:15.768 --> 22:17.637
AND WIFE.

22:17.670 --> 22:20.840
AND MAY GOD ADD HIS BLESSINGS

22:20.873 --> 22:23.576
AND KEEP YOU TO FULFILL
YOUR COVENANTS

22:23.610 --> 22:28.548
FROM HENCEFORTH AND FOREVER.

22:30.617 --> 22:32.519
AMEN.

23:04.517 --> 23:06.453
[knife being sharpened]

23:25.472 --> 23:27.674
- IT IS A TRADITION

23:27.707 --> 23:30.610
THAT THE GROOM

23:30.643 --> 23:32.845
CARVES THE PIG.

23:36.583 --> 23:38.485
- THAT WOULD BE MY PLEASURE.

23:38.518 --> 23:40.587
- [chuckles]

23:41.888 --> 23:44.924
- NOT BEFORE GRACE.

23:44.957 --> 23:47.760
- OF COURSE.

23:50.229 --> 23:52.699
HEAVENLY FATHER,

23:52.732 --> 23:55.935
TO WHOM ALL HEARTS ARE KNOWN

23:55.968 --> 23:59.739
AND NO SECRETS ARE HID,

23:59.772 --> 24:03.676
BLESS US THESE THY GIFTS

24:03.710 --> 24:06.479
THAT YOU HAVE PLACED
BEFORE US.

24:06.513 --> 24:09.516
AND THIS MAN...

24:09.549 --> 24:11.951
AND WIFE,

24:11.984 --> 24:14.887
MAY THEY LIVE A LONG

24:14.921 --> 24:17.790
AND HAPPY LIFE TOGETHER.

24:17.824 --> 24:19.826
AMEN.
- AMEN.

24:19.859 --> 24:20.960
- AMEN.
- AMEN.

24:20.993 --> 24:23.963
- AMEN.

24:23.996 --> 24:25.464
- HMM.

24:31.538 --> 24:33.806
- IT'S MY TRADITION

24:33.840 --> 24:36.843
THAT THE MEAT'S CARVED
AT A SIDE TABLE

24:36.876 --> 24:39.679
SO AS NOT TO SOIL
THE LADY'S TABLE LINEN.

24:39.712 --> 24:41.514
- THANK YOU, SON,
FOR YOUR THOUGHTFULNESS.

24:41.548 --> 24:43.883
- YOU WILL CALL HER MOTHER.

24:43.916 --> 24:46.953
AND YOU WILL CALL ME FATHER.

24:48.888 --> 24:50.990
- YES, FATHER.

25:07.039 --> 25:09.542
PIG SKIN'S SLICK.

25:09.576 --> 25:12.278
WOULDN'T STAND TOO CLOSE.

25:12.311 --> 25:14.280
MY HAND MIGHT SLIP THE BLADE
INTO YOUR LIVER.

25:14.313 --> 25:18.284
- YOU'RE A DIFFERENT MAN,
BROTHER BOHANNON...

25:18.317 --> 25:22.855
WITH A NEW WIFE
AND A CHILD ON THE WAY.

25:22.889 --> 25:26.893
- I'M STILL LIABLE TO KILL YOU.
KNOW THAT.

25:26.926 --> 25:31.063
- DON'T YOU THINK IT POSSIBLE
FOR A MAN TO CHANGE?

25:31.097 --> 25:33.099
[knife clinking]
CAN'T YOU BELIEVE...

25:33.132 --> 25:38.838
I AM NOT THE MAN I WAS?

25:38.871 --> 25:42.809
- I DON'T TRUST YOU
FARTHER THAN I CAN SPIT.

25:42.842 --> 25:44.977
- IF YOU DO NOT BELIEVE
THAT WE CAN CHANGE,

25:45.011 --> 25:49.816
HOW CAN YOU YOURSELF
BELIEVE THAT YOU HAVE CHANGED?

25:51.984 --> 25:53.986
IF I'M NOT BISHOP DUTSON,

25:54.020 --> 25:57.724
HOW CAN YOU BE
BROTHER BOHANNON?

25:57.757 --> 26:01.060
NEW SON TO THIS FAMILY,

26:01.093 --> 26:05.064
WHO DID NOT TAKE THAT KNIFE
AND PUT IT INTO MY HEART

26:05.097 --> 26:08.567
THE MOMENT I HANDED IT
TO YOU.

26:13.640 --> 26:15.808
- I MADE A PROMISE.

26:15.842 --> 26:17.810
- THE OLD BOHANNON
WOULDN'T HAVE CARED.

26:17.844 --> 26:22.782
HE WOULD AVENGE THE MURDER
OF MRS. LILY BELL.

26:25.384 --> 26:27.820
- MEAT'S COOLING.
SERVE IT.

26:31.891 --> 26:34.861
[tuba playing]

26:34.894 --> 26:42.902
*

26:46.138 --> 26:49.676
- WHAT IS THAT
INFERNAL NOISE OUTSIDE?

26:49.709 --> 26:51.077
- I'M AFRAID
YOUR CELEBRATORY BAND

26:51.110 --> 26:53.713
CONSISTS OF A SOLITARY
TUBA PLAYER.

26:53.746 --> 26:59.051
- UGH, WILL SOMEONE
PLEASE SHOOT HIM?

26:59.085 --> 27:00.186
[gunshot]

27:00.219 --> 27:01.988
[crowd gasping, tuba clanks]

27:02.021 --> 27:03.790
- YOU KNOW, DURANT,

27:03.823 --> 27:06.025
A POOR WINNER IS UNBECOMING,

27:06.058 --> 27:08.661
REGARDLESS
OF THE BATTLEFIELD.

27:08.695 --> 27:11.063
- [sighs]
ALL I WANT

27:11.097 --> 27:15.702
IS FOR THIS DAY--
THIS HOUR--TO PASS,

27:15.735 --> 27:17.670
SO I CAN RETURN TO BUILDING
MY RAILROAD.

27:17.704 --> 27:19.071
- YOU MEAN THE RAILROAD.

27:19.105 --> 27:20.740
IN THE MEANTIME,
IT'S GOOD FORM

27:20.773 --> 27:22.742
TO ACKNOWLEDGE THE RIVALS
WHO KNOCK OFF

27:22.775 --> 27:25.044
OUR ROUGH EDGES...

27:25.077 --> 27:27.146
AND SHAPE US.

27:27.179 --> 27:32.752
- DO YOU MEAN BOHANNON?

27:32.785 --> 27:34.754
BARKEEP!

27:37.924 --> 27:40.192
I WAS PLANNING A TOAST
ALL ALONG,

27:40.226 --> 27:43.195
BUT SINCE YOU INSIST.

27:48.134 --> 27:53.139
TO YOUR WORTHY WAR ENEMY...

27:53.172 --> 27:56.042
WHO CHAMPIONED THE CAUSE
OF HUMAN BONDAGE

27:56.075 --> 27:58.811
THAT TORE THIS NATION APART

27:58.845 --> 28:02.815
AND KILLED
MANY FINE YOUNG MEN.

28:06.986 --> 28:10.056
AHH.

28:10.089 --> 28:11.958
[slams shot glass on table]

28:13.960 --> 28:17.864
TO YOUR SAVIOR
OF THE RAILROAD,

28:17.897 --> 28:20.967
WHOSE ANTICS
HAVE PUT HUNTINGTON AHEAD

28:21.000 --> 28:22.802
AND US BEHIND IN THIS,

28:22.835 --> 28:27.039
THE GREATEST RACE
OF MODERN TIMES.

28:34.814 --> 28:38.851
TO YOUR MAN OF INTEGRITY,

28:38.885 --> 28:42.188
AS YOU CALL HIM
IN YOUR NEWSPAPER.

28:42.221 --> 28:45.758
APPARENTLY, HIS INTEGRITY

28:45.792 --> 28:47.226
HAS LOST HIM HIS LIFE

28:47.259 --> 28:51.097
TO MEN WHO TOOK EXCEPTION
WITH HIS INTEGRITY.

28:51.130 --> 28:56.168
- I TAKE EXCEPTION
TO THE SINCERITY OF THIS TOAST.

28:59.271 --> 29:02.241
- TO CULLEN BOHANNON, THEN.

29:02.274 --> 29:05.845
MAY GOD SPEED HIM
TO HIS JUST DESSERTS.

29:05.878 --> 29:08.214
AND TO US.

29:08.247 --> 29:13.886
MAY GOD BLESS US ALL
AS WE DRIVE OUR STEEL FORWARD

29:13.920 --> 29:18.157
INTO THE WAXY HEART
OF THE CENTRAL PACIFIC.

29:18.190 --> 29:20.759
- HEAR, HEAR.
- HEAR, HEAR.

29:48.320 --> 29:52.224
[horse whinnying]

29:52.258 --> 29:54.360
[growling]

29:54.393 --> 29:57.596
- WHOA, COME BACK HERE!
GET BACK HERE! WHOA!

29:57.629 --> 29:59.298
[growling]

29:59.331 --> 30:01.400
[roars]

30:03.903 --> 30:05.037
[roars]

30:05.071 --> 30:07.106
[gunshots]

30:07.139 --> 30:08.574
[click]

30:08.607 --> 30:09.575
UHH!

30:09.608 --> 30:12.311
[roars]

30:12.344 --> 30:13.913
HYAH! HYAH!

30:13.946 --> 30:15.047
HYAH!

30:15.081 --> 30:16.115
[screams]

30:17.917 --> 30:21.187
[water sloshing]

30:21.220 --> 30:23.255
- [sighs]

31:06.698 --> 31:08.434
HOW OLD ARE YOU?

31:08.467 --> 31:10.636
- 18.

31:10.669 --> 31:12.404
19 NEXT MONTH.

31:15.674 --> 31:17.309
- I DON'T RECKON
THIS IS HOW YOU FIGURED

31:17.343 --> 31:20.980
ON SPENDING
YOUR WEDDING NIGHT.

31:21.013 --> 31:22.448
- MOTHER SAID
NOBODY'D WANT ME

31:22.481 --> 31:26.285
SINCE I WAS UNCHASTE.

31:26.318 --> 31:28.354
NEVER THOUGHT I'D EVEN HAVE
A WEDDING NIGHT.

31:28.387 --> 31:30.289
- [grunts]

31:30.322 --> 31:32.925
NEVER THOUGHT I'D HAVE
MORE THAN ONE MYSELF.

31:43.069 --> 31:45.071
- WHAT WAS IT LIKE?

31:49.441 --> 31:54.013
- MM, IT'S WHAT YOU
COULD IMAGINE, I SUPPOSE.

31:54.046 --> 31:56.015
GOT MARRIED IN A BIG CHURCH
IN NEW YORK

31:56.048 --> 31:57.349
AND THEN TOOK A TRIP
UP TO THE MOUNTAINS.

31:57.383 --> 32:00.452
- NO, THE--
THE WEDDING NIGHT.

32:04.290 --> 32:06.325
- THAT'S KIND OF PERSONAL.

32:08.327 --> 32:11.430
- YOU'RE MY HUSBAND.

32:11.463 --> 32:13.465
- YEAH.

32:16.368 --> 32:19.205
WELL...

32:21.307 --> 32:23.375
FOR ONE THING, WE HAD--

32:23.409 --> 32:28.014
HADN'T BEEN CHASTE
ABOUT IT.

32:28.047 --> 32:31.083
- THAT'S A SIN.

32:31.117 --> 32:32.151
[both snicker]

32:32.184 --> 32:34.253
- YEAH.

32:34.286 --> 32:36.288
MARY WAS A LOT OF FUN.

32:41.193 --> 32:44.730
- ARE YOU GONNA LEAVE ME
ONCE YOU CAN?

32:44.763 --> 32:46.498
- NO.

32:50.236 --> 32:54.073
I AIN'T LIKE THAT.

32:54.106 --> 32:57.209
- WHAT IF I'M NOT FUN?

32:57.243 --> 33:00.146
- SEEM TO RECALL US
HAVING FUN IN THAT BARN.

33:04.183 --> 33:07.986
- WHAT IF I'M NOT FUN
ANYMORE TO YOU?

33:11.390 --> 33:14.126
- IT'S BEEN MY EXPERIENCE...

33:14.160 --> 33:17.096
THAT THE FUN WILL COME.

33:35.447 --> 33:37.516
- MORNING.

33:37.549 --> 33:42.054
- THESE LOOK MORE LIKE CHURCH
CLOTHES THAN WORK CLOTHES.

33:42.088 --> 33:44.090
- IT'S WHAT THE MEN WEAR.

34:09.148 --> 34:10.382
[sets bowl down]

34:30.402 --> 34:32.471
- WE'LL FIGURE IT OUT
TOGETHER.

34:45.351 --> 34:50.356
[overlapping chatter]

34:57.429 --> 34:59.465
[women laughing]

35:15.581 --> 35:19.451
- QUITE A STEP-UP
FROM THE MUD HOLE SHIT PIT

35:19.485 --> 35:21.220
I ALLOWED YOU TO ESCAPE FROM.

35:21.253 --> 35:22.921
[chuckles]

35:22.954 --> 35:25.657
GAMING TABLES...

35:25.691 --> 35:27.459
NEW WOMEN...

35:27.493 --> 35:32.198
REAL WHISKEY.

35:32.231 --> 35:35.601
- I'LL TAKE THE SHOP, THEN,
NEXT DOOR AS WELL.

35:35.634 --> 35:39.471
FOR MY CAMPAIGN HEADQUARTERS.

35:39.505 --> 35:41.640
[whispering]
CONSIDER IT A DONATION

35:41.673 --> 35:43.942
IN MY STANDING FOR MAYOR.

35:43.975 --> 35:46.645
- [scoffs]

35:46.678 --> 35:50.916
I DETERMINE
WHO'S MAYOR HERE.

35:50.949 --> 35:55.654
THAT IS WHY
YOU ARE RUNNING UNOPPOSED.

35:55.687 --> 35:58.724
THAT'S MY CONTRIBUTION.

36:04.463 --> 36:07.299
- SO I CAN COUNT
ON YOUR VOTE THEN?

36:07.333 --> 36:10.436
- MY VOTE IS THE ONLY VOTE
THAT COUNTS.

36:23.582 --> 36:25.951
YOU WILL BE THE ONLY
FEMALE EDITOR

36:25.984 --> 36:29.588
OF A DAILY NEWSPAPER
IN THE ENTIRE COUNTRY.

36:34.260 --> 36:37.629
YOU'RE WELCOME.

36:37.663 --> 36:40.232
- I HAVEN'T SAID YES.

36:40.266 --> 36:42.268
YET.

36:44.470 --> 36:47.739
- YOU'RE NOT GOING TO SAY NO.

36:56.615 --> 36:59.551
- THOSE ARE RAILROAD WORKERS.

36:59.585 --> 37:03.589
WE'RE BUILDING OUR OWN
SPUR LINE TO THE SOUTH.

37:03.622 --> 37:06.392
- CROSSED MY MIND THAT'S WHY
THE MORMONS KIDNAPPED ME.

37:06.425 --> 37:08.727
- MM, BROTHER HATCH
WANTED TO HANG YOU,

37:08.760 --> 37:12.264
NOT PUT YOU TO WORK.

37:15.767 --> 37:17.669
- SAME AS YOU.

37:17.703 --> 37:19.605
- YES.

37:19.638 --> 37:22.474
BUT HEAVENLY FATHER HAS
MORE APPROPRIATE LABORS FOR YOU,

37:22.508 --> 37:25.611
BROTHER BOHANNON.

37:25.644 --> 37:31.417
- * BOOKS OF MOSES

37:31.450 --> 37:33.819
- LIFT!

37:33.852 --> 37:35.487
- COME ON, FELLAS.

37:35.521 --> 37:36.788
- NICE AND SLOW!
- BRING IT IN HERE, BOY.

37:36.822 --> 37:38.457
- * WET IN THE WATER

37:38.490 --> 37:39.558
- KEEP IT STRAIGHT.

37:39.591 --> 37:41.026
- * WEEPING IN THE SUN

37:41.059 --> 37:45.030
- BRING IT RIGHT ON IN.
GET THEM TIES READY.

37:45.063 --> 37:46.432
THERE WE GO.

37:46.465 --> 37:48.066
GONNA LOCK THAT IN.

37:48.099 --> 37:49.668
- LOCK THAT DOWN.
- BRING IT ON IN THERE.

37:49.701 --> 37:51.370
- * GOT SOME SPLINTERS

37:51.403 --> 37:52.571
- AH, YOU THERE.

37:52.604 --> 37:56.041
BIG FELLA.
WHAT'S YOUR NAME?

37:56.074 --> 37:58.410
- THEY CALL ME PSALMS,
MR. DURANT.

37:58.444 --> 38:00.045
- PSALMS, PSALMS.

38:00.078 --> 38:03.349
YOU MAKE SURE YOUR PEOPLE
PUT THEIR BACKS INTO IT.

38:03.382 --> 38:04.783
I'M BEHIND SCHEDULE.

38:04.816 --> 38:06.418
- * FLAMING HEART

38:06.452 --> 38:07.753
- YES, SIR!

38:07.786 --> 38:10.422
*

38:10.456 --> 38:12.658
- * BEATING SWIFT

38:12.691 --> 38:15.361
- NO GOOD WHITE DEVIL...

38:15.394 --> 38:17.563
PUT HIS HEEL ON MY NECK.

38:17.596 --> 38:19.798
BETTER WATCH OUT.

38:19.831 --> 38:25.537
- * AT YOUR FEET

38:25.571 --> 38:32.478
*

