DIDN'T YOU *

39:52.190 --> 39:56.161
* BOOKS OF MOSES
BROUGHT ME *

39:56.194 --> 39:59.765
* RIGHT HERE BACK TO YOU

39:59.798 --> 40:02.668
*

40:02.701 --> 40:07.205
* FLAMING HEART

40:07.238 --> 40:12.444
* AIN'T IT SWEET

40:12.478 --> 40:17.716
* LIGHTING THE WORLD

40:17.749 --> 40:22.521
* AT YOUR FEET

